          "type": "html",
          "settings": {
            "code": "<div class=\"mt-5 text-center\">\n<span class=\"subtop\">ANCIENT BLISS</span>\n<h3>TAKE CARE OF YOUR TEMPLE</h3>\n<div class=\"row justify-content-center mt-3 mb-5\">\n<p class=\"col-lg-8\">The Ancient Bliss community aims to educate and empower you through herbal supplements that honor indigenous<br> wisdom, inspiring you to reconnect with your body’s natural state and take care of your temple.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
